                                 <note>
                                    <foreign xml:lang="en">There are seven stanzas, the following is the first:</foreign>
                                 </note>
                                 <lb/>ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ መምሕረ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወምዑዘ፡ ምግባር፡ እምኮል።
